{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_52_02",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "目指すは『あの人』の新刊……！！\n待ってて、ペト君、ダラーテ！",
      "startTime": 3.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……おはよう、優。さっきから一人で何やってるんだ？",
      "startTime": 6.6999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5047387759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？　こんな朝早くになんで\nえっと、その……いつから見てたんです？",
      "startTime": 15.9047387759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.9047387759
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくの旅先だし、たまには散歩でもと思ってな\n「うーん！　天気もええし」ってところから見てたよ",
      "startTime": 25.2666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5480491955
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5480491955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "最初からやん！　なんで声かけないで見てるんです！？\n……こほん、まぁええです。何やってるのか、でしたね",
      "startTime": 36.5147158622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.2813835461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちはこれから北海道最大の即売会イベント\n『こみぱに！　in北海道』に行くんです！",
      "startTime": 46.7813835461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "一番の目玉は、幻の同人作家『コン・サド』さんの\n新刊です。あ、コン・サドさんは知ってますよね？",
      "startTime": 54.4813835461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1147161166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "前衛的にして衝撃的な作風の一方、元ネタへの愛も凄い\nうちらの界隈やと、伝説的な作家さんなんです",
      "startTime": 64.6147161166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.5813782055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "姿を現すのは北海道の即売会だけで、付いたあだ名が\n『レジェンドオブレジェンドオブレジェンド』",
      "startTime": 73.5480494499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.281372102
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "誰が付けたんだ、そのあだ名……。それはともかく\n同人誌即売会ってのは、こんなに朝早いんだな",
      "startTime": 80.1000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "始まるんは大体午前九時とか十時です。でも\n今日のは全国から人が集まる超大型イベントなんよ！",
      "startTime": 89.3500636737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.1833924293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "だから早く行って入場列に並ばんと……\n人気の本は一瞬で売り切れてしまうんです！",
      "startTime": 98.0167303403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.516721185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか。俺はこの間優達が参加した即売会しか\n知らないから、詳しいことは分からないけど……",
      "startTime": 106.2333288829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "売る人と買う人、参加する人全員の一体感に感動したよ\n騒ぎにならないよう気を付けて楽しんでくれ",
      "startTime": 115.933327357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.2035466194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、さすが{user}さんや\n同人誌即売会のこと、よう分かっとる",
      "startTime": 122.9702178638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "即売会は、おんなじ好きを持った同志が集まって\n一体になる……ライブそのものなんです！",
      "startTime": 130.4271626178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.1702132861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "みなまで言わんでも分かります\n{user}さん、一緒に行きたいんやろ？",
      "startTime": 137.1368845304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.8368799527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、今日はうちが即売会の楽しさを手取り足取り\nたーっくさん、教えてあげますね！",
      "startTime": 145.5368845304,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7196.4489301000185,
          "startTime": 152.7333334605
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9919.78226340001,
          "startTime": 155.4566667938
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.6368799527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え……もしかして、俺も一緒に行く流れなのか？\n待ってくれ、優。服を引っ張らないでくれ……",
      "startTime": 154.1666667938,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4965.428702099985,
          "startTime": 159.1320954959
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.8820954959
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.8820954959
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "うち……北海道の即売会を舐めとったかもしれん……\n『もんバケ』の本を出しとるサークルがこんなに！？",
      "startTime": 164.9321000736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.9321000736
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "しかもペト君の同人誌も大量やん！　はぁ～\n天国とは、はるか北の大地にあったんやねぇ……",
      "startTime": 174.4654186567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.9320853233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "『もんバケ』って……確か『週刊ラッキー』で\n連載してる人気漫画だよな。俺も読んだことがあるよ",
      "startTime": 183.6000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.0580717404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "それならこれ、読んでみて下さい！\nこの作家さんのもんバケの同人誌、凄いんです！",
      "startTime": 191.3247531574,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10933.320108999993,
          "startTime": 202.2580732664
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.3913918495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "元々は敵同士だったペト君とダラーテの心の機微が\n凄～く細やかに描かれてるんよ。このページとか……",
      "startTime": 199.2914065998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.3580473263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "……あぁ～！　なんやこのセリフ！？\n「一晩だけなら、お前を受け入れてやってもいい……」",
      "startTime": 208.4580620766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.9580473263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんだいきなり……\n突然大声を出してどうしたんだ、優？",
      "startTime": 214.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.8097827594
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
